# Minimal synthetic mesh fixture (not game data) — one textured, normaled triangle. Used by
# CI to smoke-test obj-to-mesh -> mesh-to-obj round-tripping without needing licensed game
# assets: if obj-to-mesh's output doesn't re-parse via mesh-to-obj, this is where it'll show.
mtllib triangle.mtl
o TestObject
v 0.0 0.0 0.0
v 1.0 0.0 0.0
v 0.0 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 0.0
vt 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 1.0
vn 0.0 0.0 1.0
usemtl TestMat
f 1/1/1 2/2/1 3/3/1
